{"tid":1752903,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老母班狗 覺唔覺得自己好撚柒","createTime":"2019-11-25T00:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T00:44:05.000Z","uid":313187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d86c0646661fe68bd82a24927b7df7c340e9f52","tid":1752903,"uid":313187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:25:30.000Z","msg":"警方周三(20日)在理大外「開咪」，稱：「原來你哋妒忌，原來你哋連讀毅進嘅毅力都無，毅進係有毅力，要有進步先讀到，讀完之後你哋就可以攞到二萬五千蚊做一個警員嘞，你呢？」警員又指，留守示威者薪水低、破壞中大及理大，直言：「你哋妒忌警察！」<br />\n<br />\n警員又「嗌咪」，指留守者「憎人富貴嫌人貧」，「你哋睇下24號嘅投票結果會係點！民意逆轉！」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意逆轉呢? 傻閪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a837452fa2ae4851bbb0c4c9ee6975119895ac3","tid":1752903,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"逆轉左lo,不過由佢個邊逆過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}